## Catalog rule

`catalog/` holds document types, parse/serialize, and manifest data ‚Äî **no registry writes, no spawn logic**.

| Belongs in `catalog/` | Belongs outside `catalog/` |
|-----------------------|----------------------------|
| `PropDocument` / `ActorDocument` types + parse/serialize | `spawnPropEditor`, `spawnActorEditor` |
| `CONSTRUCT_KEYS` component key strings | `install*System` |
| `KaykitManifest` types, `loadKaykitManifest`, tree filters | `bootstrap` composition |
| Document ‚Üî `PropDefinition`/`ActorDefinition` converters | Session slices (`session/*`) |
| `slugifyDocumentId` | UI hooks, React components |

**`catalog/` must not import from `entities/`, `session/`, `scenes/`, `globals/`, or `ui/`.**

## Entity rule

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `entities/editorCommon/` | Shared mechanics: origin marker, collider shape resources, `editableTarget`, `editorSelection`, materials, TRS, `syncPartLocal` |
| `entities/actorEditor/` | Actor root/character/attachment/collider components + `spawnActor*` + `installActorColliderFollowSystem` |
| `entities/propEditor/` | Prop root/part components + `spawnAssetPart`/`spawnColliderPart`/`spawnPropEditor` |
| `entities/gizmos/` | Move/scale/rotate gizmo meshes, picking, input, `installConstructGizmoSystem` |
| `entities/orbit/` | Orbit camera state, origin marker, anim preview entity, `installConstructOrbitSystem` |

Shared editor mechanics (used by both prop and actor editors) live in `entities/editorCommon/` ‚Äî never duplicate origin marker, collider, or TRS logic per-editor.

## Session rule

- `session/types.ts` ‚Äî `ConstructSession`, `ConstructSessionState`, `ConstructSessionDeps` types + `createConstructSessionState`
- `session/preview.ts` ‚Äî standalone asset preview load/texture-variant slice
- `session/propEditor.ts` ‚Äî prop document mutation slice (add/remove/rename/update parts)
- `session/actorEditor.ts` ‚Äî actor document mutation slice (character/attachments/colliders)
- `session/anim.ts` ‚Äî animation pack load/apply/clear slice

Session slices are pure functions of `(deps, state, ...)` returning updated documents ‚Äî no React, no JSX. System installers live in `scenes/installEditorSystems.ts`; session slices call those helpers instead of importing `install*System` directly.

## Globals rule

`globals/bootstrap.ts` composes engine primitives (render pipeline + `installEditorSceneSystems`) into a `ConstructSession` ‚Äî composition only, no document mutation logic (that lives in `session/`).

## Storage rule

- `storage/localStore.ts` ‚Äî generic `createLocalStore<TDoc>(storageKey)` factory (list/get/save/remove)
- `storage/actorLocalStore.ts` / `storage/propLocalStore.ts` ‚Äî thin wrappers binding the factory to `ActorDocument`/`PropDocument` with a storage-clone function

Do not reimplement read/write/list/remove localStorage logic per document type ‚Äî extend `localStore.ts`.

## UI rule

- `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx` ‚Äî layout shell only: panels, modals wiring, mode switch UI. Delegates lifecycle and workflow logic to `ui/app/useConstruct*.ts` hooks
- `ui/app/useConstructSession.ts` ‚Äî bootstrap lifecycle, session ref, prop/actor document state + listeners
- `ui/app/useManifestExplorer.ts` ‚Äî manifest load, asset/character trees, explorer search + expand state
- `ui/app/useConstructViewer.ts` ‚Äî preview model loading, texture variant + animation preview state
- `ui/app/useConstructMode.ts` ‚Äî mode + transform-mode state, tab-cycle input, enter-prop/actor-mode effect
- `ui/app/useConstructSelection.ts` ‚Äî selected prop part / actor selection state
- `ui/app/useConstructDocumentActions.ts` ‚Äî New/Save/Load/Import/Export/Rename workflows + modals
- `ui/app/useConstructAssetActions.ts` ‚Äî add asset/character/collider from the explorer
- `ui/app/useConstructInspectorActions.ts` ‚Äî per-field edit handlers wired into `PropDetails`/`ActorDetails`
- UI talks only to `ConstructSession` (via `bootstrap`) or catalog document helpers ‚Äî **never import `entities/` from `ui/`**
- `ui/inspector/shared.tsx` ‚Äî shared `AxisRow`, `DetailsHeader`, `formatNum`/`parseNum` for `PropDetails`/`ActorDetails`

## Forbidden

- Barrel `index.ts` anywhere under `construct/src/`
- Comments in agent-generated `.ts`/`.tsx` source
- God objects in `globals/bootstrap.ts` or `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx` ‚Äî one concern per file/hook
- Component key strings outside `catalog/keys/components.ts`
- Duplicated `AxisRow`/`formatNum`/`parseNum`/rename-header JSX across inspector panels ‚Äî use `ui/inspector/shared.tsx`
- Duplicated localStorage read/write/list/remove logic across `storage/*LocalStore.ts` ‚Äî use `storage/localStore.ts`
- `entities/` imports from `ui/`
